divs: Sighting Detailsi was looking out my backdoor patio door on 12-14-2012 around 7pm that night normally their is a airport called flimming field iam on the opposite end of the airport and as my house faces i was looking towards saint paul,mn. planes come in to the small airport daily but this was different these objects came from like the woodbury way as i was looking out i saw something i hadnt seen before so i opened the back sliding door to get a closer look and thats when i saw two objects that had some soft lights all around it and as the objects aproched they were about tree line level and they stopped short and made a quick turn around and zipped away back the same way . so then i came in and screamed to my wife that i had seem something strange so i ran into my wifes bedroom and looked out her window towards flemming field where the airport is and didnt see anything so i went into my bedroom and got my binoclurs and my night vision.so i preceded back to the patio door and starting looking through them . so as i stood there here and behold here they come again as i stand there watchin they did them the same things ,they came up from the woodbury way and did the exact same thing again so i screemed at my wife again went to her window and nothing . so that was what i seen . yea normally the planes come from the saint paul way and u have no problems seeing them comming in and u can see their lights at nighttime,but this is something i have never seen before with my eyes.
Summary: two objects i saw while looking out my back patio door last night had some soft colors flutter
